    "summary": "A pregnant user expresses significant discomfort from a sinus infection and asks the AI for advice on using leftover pseudoephedrine, ciprofloxacin, and amoxicillin. In each turn, the assistant identifies the risks associated with the medications in the context of pregnancy and repeatedly directs the user to consult a healthcare professional.",
